    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Embark on a narrative adventure across the world of <i>Shippin</i>!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/e7a81c7d94ee5fd7400e17c403136de2.poster.avif?t=1770061586\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/e7a81c7d94ee5fd7400e17c403136de2.webm?t=1770061586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/e7a81c7d94ee5fd7400e17c403136de2.mp4?t=1770061586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Salva, a lost sailor driven by the desire to uncover how he ended up in these mysterious regions and uncharted seas.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the mysteries of the ocean!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/e10597214e022dd3cc58522bc9139331.poster.avif?t=1770061586\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/e10597214e022dd3cc58522bc9139331.webm?t=1770061586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/e10597214e022dd3cc58522bc9139331.mp4?t=1770061586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With nothing but your wits, your ship, and a bit of luck, you’ll set out on a mission to uncover and resolve the source of the evil plaguing every port you visit.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover stories along your journey</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/51372f571704c7daf6d27c3fe10b83fa.poster.avif?t=1770061586\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/51372f571704c7daf6d27c3fe10b83fa.webm?t=1770061586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/51372f571704c7daf6d27c3fe10b83fa.mp4?t=1770061586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade tales and unravel the secrets behind the different peoples who shaped this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>DISCLAIMER</strong>:</i> <i>There are jokes in this game.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use your tools to help the inhabitants of the various ports<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/d681df6f0816c6a3acdccb2c12bc536e.poster.avif?t=1770061586\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/d681df6f0816c6a3acdccb2c12bc536e.webm?t=1770061586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334100/extras/d681df6f0816c6a3acdccb2c12bc536e.mp4?t=1770061586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade and use your ship tools to face every challenge, helping the people of each port as you uncover the stories that defined their regions.</p>",
